::Feline::

"I don't know where Skulletron is.  I lost touch with him. But , yes, 
I did bring HotRod, Rodimus Prime to you. And Battera and 
Cybershark.  They will follow you.  HotRod has all the info, plus 
what I have for you."  She looked at Zardus and smiled,"When you have 
a moment, I will need to speak to you alone."





--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Zardus::
> 
> Zardus nods. "Excellent. Much more than I expected..."
> 
> He looks at Cybershark and Hot Rod. He had had plenty of time to 
look 
> at history logs during the brief period of time when he had been a 
> Predacon. He knew who Hot Rod was, or at least who the original Hot 
> Rod was.
> 
> "Two new troops... Plus Battera. And," he looks at Hot Rod, "If I 
am 
> not mistaken, this is Rodimus?"
> 
> Zardus turns back to Feline, "But did you get the information on 
the 
> Cybertronian Fire? And where is Skulletron?"
> 
> 
> --- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, logomorph@h... wrote:
